item.title: Prayer bpn13067 in Hiri Motu
item.description: Momokani lau hereva lauegu Dirava e, Oi ese lau Oi karaia Oi lau diba bona lau tomadiho henia totona. Lau gwauraia, harihari, lauegu manoka bona Oiemu goada dekenai, lauegu ogogami bona Oiemu kohu dekenai. Dirava ta be lasi, Oi sibona, Durua Dika dekenai, Sibona Noho Diravana. (Source category: DINA IBOUNAI KARAIA GURIGURI KWADOGINA) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 13067)
